{
  "stem": "26609.21",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later was little brother of 13, that he was killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said, if you don't stop crying, I don't know what I will do with you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't want to say why she is crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She just said, because I don't know anything about my family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't want to say this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20 Years after the war already went, his parents lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they all liked her very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She couldn't tell him, because he would never accept if she is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe he felt something, I don't, she doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he never, he never would say anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when I arrived there, and in so many years after the war, and I said, why are you afraid?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We haven't got any more afraid?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why are you afraid to say, I'm Jewish?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, don't tell it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you want to stay as not Jewish here, you can stay in my place as long as you wish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I said him, if I have to hide my name and hide myself as a, as a non-Jewess, I better leave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I won't stay here with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think he got a heart attack, because he was, you know, worrying all the time, because I said it open.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people knew later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said it open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, why do I have to hide, again here, in France?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And said, you hate Jews?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said no, but my wife is not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You knew that she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think he didn't go to work because he was ashamed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll continue next tape.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
